        <!-- FAQ 1 -->
        <div class="collapse collapse-plus bg-base-200">
          <input type="radio" name="faq-accordion" checked="checked" />
          <div class="collapse-title text-xl font-medium">
            Do you offer free shipping?
          </div>
          <div class="collapse-content">
            <p>Yes! We offer free shipping on all orders over $50. For orders under $50, standard shipping rates apply. All orders are processed within 1-2 business days.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- FAQ 2 -->
        <div class="collapse collapse-plus bg-base-200">
          <input type="radio" name="faq-accordion" />
          <div class="collapse-title text-xl font-medium">
            What is your return policy?
          </div>
          <div class="collapse-content">
            <p>We offer a 30-day money-back guarantee. If you're not completely satisfied with your purchase, you can return it within 30 days for a full refund. Items must be unused and in original packaging.</p>
