        </div>

        <!-- FAQ 3 -->
        <div class="collapse collapse-plus bg-base-200">
          <input type="radio" name="faq-accordion" />
          <div class="collapse-title text-xl font-medium">
            How can I track my order?
          </div>
          <div class="collapse-content">
            <p>Once your order ships, you'll receive a tracking number via email. You can use this number to track your package on our website or through the carrier's tracking system.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- FAQ 4 -->
        <div class="collapse collapse-plus bg-base-200">
          <input type="radio" name="faq-accordion" />
          <div class="collapse-title text-xl font-medium">
            What payment methods do you accept?
          </div>
          <div class="collapse-content">
            <p>We accept all major credit cards (Visa, MasterCard, American Express, Discover), Apple Pay, Google Pay, and other digital payment methods through our secure Stripe payment processor.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- FAQ 5 -->
        <div class="collapse collapse-plus bg-base-200">
          <input type="radio" name="faq-accordion" />
          <div class="collapse-title text-xl font-medium">
            Are your products authentic?
          </div>
          <div class="collapse-content">
            <p>Absolutely! We source all our products directly from verified manufacturers and authorized distributors. Every item comes with a certificate of authenticity and is backed by our quality guarantee.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- FAQ 6 -->
        <div class="collapse collapse-plus bg-base-200">
          <input type="radio" name="faq-accordion" />
          <div class="collapse-title text-xl font-medium">
